ADDITIONAL USE NOTICE (non-binding, important):

m3dsEYE performs automatic number-plate recognition (ANPR) and processes
personal data. It is intended ONLY for use by authorised law-enforcement or
government bodies acting under lawful authority. Operators are solely
responsible for ensuring their deployment complies with all applicable laws
(e.g. data-protection / privacy legislation, surveillance and evidence law).
Do not deploy for public facial recognition or covert/unauthorised tracking.
